HEADWORD: Monkfish
<hw>Monk"fish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The angel fish (<gen>Squatina</gen>).</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>The angler (<gen>Lophius</gen>), esp. the goosefishes
<spn>Lophius Americanus</spn> in America and <spn>Lophius
piscatorius</spn> in Europe, used for food.</def> <au>[MW10]</au>⟦br⟧
